> Hi all
> I just picked up a 1979 Westy a couple weeks ago and
> need advice on my dash EGR light. How do I switch it
> off ??
> This is an all original 2000FI engine.

Remove the left front kickpanel. Follow the speedo cable down to a black box.
Press the little reset button in with a little screwdriver. Wait 30000 miles for
the light to come back on.......

